          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-1-1724229726732-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>fries</strong> and <strong>chopped rosemary </strong>to a <strong>baking paper</strong>-lined baking tray (or two!) with a small drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray[s] in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp – these are your <strong>rosemary fries</strong></p>",
