    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>tomato[es] </strong>roughly</p><p>Wash your <strong>lettuce</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper and roughly shred</p><p>Add the <strong>shredded lettuce </strong>and <strong>chopped tomato </strong>to a large bowl with the <strong>remaining balsamic vinegar</strong> and toss until coated – this is your <strong>tomato salad</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
