      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drizzle the <strong>rosemary fries </strong>with your <strong>truffle oil </strong>(not a fan of truffle? Just add a little!)<strong> </strong>and top with the <strong>grated Italian hard cheese </strong>– these are your <strong>cheesy rosemary &</strong> <strong>truffle fries</strong></p><p>Fill each<strong> garlic bread bun </strong>with a<strong> meat-free hot dog sausage </strong>and top with the <strong>balsamic caramelised onion</strong>, then serve the <strong>tomato salad</strong> and <strong>cheesy rosemary &</strong> <strong>truffle fries </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
